txt.en: A scout-warrior leads the Draig-lûth search party.\n\nDefeat the Draig-lûth scout-warrior.
You have defeated a Draig-lûth scout-warrior.\n\nReturn to Marget.
'The folks back in Brundir must be furious with us if they're sending scout-warriors.'
A few particularly strong lieutenants are leading the search for Eluna. Disrupt the search by defeating either one.
'I spied two particularly tough warriors among the chaff.\n\n'Take down either one and it'll disrupt their whole force.'
